videos.description: Miles Bridges gets the ball from Cassius Winston and then makes the lay-in to extend the Spartans lead.
videos.headline: Bridges makes tough crossover-layup

videos.description: Miles Bridges lobs the ball up and Nick Ward flies through the air to score for the Spartans.
videos.headline: Ward finishes amazing Superman-esque shot

videos.description: Jacob Calloway stays hot from behind the arc and puts the Thunderbirds within 5 points of the Spartans.
videos.headline: Calloway drains 3-pointer to close gap vs. No. 3 Michigan State

videos.description: Jaren Jackson Jr. blocks a Southern Utah shot and the Spartans score on the other end to extend their lead.
videos.headline: Jackson Jr. makes timely block

videos.description: Miles Bridges works his way around his defender and lays it in for a Spartans' score.
videos.headline: Bridges beats defender with reverse layup
